    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just more than that though. it's not about 'reevaluating' stuff. it's just that i look at my life and i see nothing. no connection, no impact. nothing. it's like i'm already a ghost. does it even matter if the ghost stays or finally just... leaves?",
